params.sqlcmd: "select " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" as \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ISSUE_INST_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_CMPLT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"ISSUE_CMPLT_DATE\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\" as \\"ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.\\"OPR_INST_CD\\" as \\"OPR_INST_CD\\", " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"OPR_INST_CD\\" as \\"OPR_INST_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WORK_ODR_CD\\" as \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\" as \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" as \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"OD_NO\\" as \\"OD_NO\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" as \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_OD.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\") as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\") as \\"ISSUE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_OD, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\" >(0) " +" and M_ITEM.\\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\" = ? " +"order by " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\""

"select " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" as \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ISSUE_INST_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_CMPLT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"ISSUE_CMPLT_DATE\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\" as \\"ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.\\"OPR_INST_CD\\" as \\"OPR_INST_CD\\", " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"OPR_INST_CD\\" as \\"OPR_INST_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WORK_ODR_CD\\" as \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\" as \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" as \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"OD_NO\\" as \\"OD_NO\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" as \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_OD.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\") as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\") as \\"ISSUE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_OD, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD(+) " +" " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\" > (0) " +" and (T_ISSUE_INST.CONS_TYP not in (1) " +" or T_ISSUE_INST.PUCH_ODR_CD is null " +" or T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD is not null) " +" and ( " +" ( " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.OPR_INST_CD like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD " +" ) or ( " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.OPR_INST_CD like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD " +" ) " +" ) " +" and M_ITEM.LOT_CTRL_FLG = ? " +"order by T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\""
"select " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_DATE_CTRL.\\"BUSINESS_OPR_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"BUSINESS_OPR_DATE\\" " +"from " +" SYS_DATE_CTRL " +"where " +" SYS_DATE_CTRL.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"from " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM'"

"insert into " +" T_RCV_ISSUE(\\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_TYP\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_QTY\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_DATE\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_GNR_TYP\\", \\"STOCK_UPD_TYP\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\", \\"OD_NO\\", \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_COMMENT\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"CONS_TYP\\",\\"LOT_NO\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_DATE(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"

"select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_TYP\\" as \\"WH_TYP\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" T_ITEM_STOCK " +"where " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(THIS_MONTH, 'YYYY/MM'), 'YYYY/MM') AS THIS_MONTH " +"FROM " +" SYS_DEBT_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ( " +" SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +" FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" )"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(INSTALL_FLG) AS INSTALL_FLG " +"FROM " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS " +"WHERE " +" OPTION_ID = 'C*'"

"insert into " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS(\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"ISSUE_DATE\\", \\"ISSUE_QTY\\", \\"UNIT_COST\\", \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\", \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", \\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\", \\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\", \\"RETURNED_GNR_TYP\\", \\"AP_PROC_TYP\\", \\"LOT_NO\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, null, ?, 1, 0, ?)"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST\\", 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" as \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"ONEROUS_FLG\\") as \\"ONEROUS_FLG\\" " +"from " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" <= TO_DATE(?) " +"order by " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" desc"
"SELECT " +" VALUE " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" NAME = ?"
"SELECT " +" PROC_EXEC_DATE " +"FROM " +" SYS_ACTUAL_COST_CTRL_AC " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ?"

"select " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO, " +" to_char(T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as ISSUE_QTY, " +" to_char(T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as ISSUE_DATE, " +" to_char(T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, " +" to_char(T_LOT_STOCK.DEFECT_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as DEFECT_QTY, " +" to_char((T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY - T_LOT_STOCK.ALCD_QTY), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as ALLOCABLE_QTY, " +" T_LOT_CTRL.EXTERNAL_LOT_NO, " +" to_char(T_LOT_CTRL.BEST_BEFORE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as BEST_BEFORE_DATE, " +" to_char(T_LOT_CTRL.PRD_CMPLT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as PRD_CMPLT_DATE, " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT " +"from " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_LOT_STOCK, " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and(T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY - T_LOT_STOCK.ALCD_QTY) <> 0 " +"order by " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO"
"UPDATE " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST " +"SET " +" ISSUE_QTY = DECODE(SIGN(ISSUE_QTY - to_number(?)), -1,0,ISSUE_QTY - to_number(?)) " +"WHERE " +" ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" AND LOT_NO = ?"

"select " +" T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO " +"from " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"where " +" T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD"

"SELECT " +" NVL(CASE WHEN TO_DATE(?,'YYYY/MM/DD') > T_LOT_CTRL.\\"BEST_BEFORE_DATE\\" " +" THEN '1' ELSE '0' END, 0) BBD_c_FLG " +"FROM " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD " +" AND T_LOT_CTRL.\\"LOT_NO\\" = ? " +" AND T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +""
"SELECT " +" ISSUE_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" AND LOT_NO = ?"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_OD, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\" >(0) " +" and(T_ISSUE_INST.CONS_TYP not in (1) " +" or T_ISSUE_INST.PUCH_ODR_CD is null " +" or T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD is not null) " +" and((T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.OPR_INST_CD like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD) " +" or (T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.OPR_INST_CD like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD)) " +" and M_ITEM.LOT_CTRL_FLG = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= NVL(TO_NUMBER(?),ROWNUM) + 1"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_OD, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\" >(0) " +" and M_ITEM.\\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\" = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"select " +" COUNT(1) " +"from " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_LOT_STOCK, " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and(T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY - T_LOT_STOCK.ALCD_QTY) <> 0 " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"
"SELECT " +" MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +"AND LOT_NO = ? " +"FOR UPDATE NOWAIT"
